cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the task of semantic segmentation. It may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it proposes a new network architecture and loss function. Additionally, it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories as it deals with portrait segmentation, which is a common task in multimedia and graphics applications.
